data.description: ** MOTIVATED SELLER ** This property is ready for your personal touch and updates. Nestled in a serene neighborhood w a split bedroom design that maximizes privacy, this home is drenched in natural light, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere. As you enter, an open living area welcomes you. The spacious kitchen w ample cabinet & counter space seamlessly flows into the second living area, highlighted by a brick fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance for relaxation & gatherings. The primary bedroom is a serene retreat w an ensuite boasting a jetted tub, separate shower, dual sinks, & walkin closet. Two secondary bedrooms share a well-placed bathroom & a nearby laundry room enhances convenience. Step outside to the covered porch, ideal for morning coffees, barbecues or simply enjoying your private backyard. Enjoy community perks like a pool, playground & picnic area. Nearby attractions include Willow Creek Park, Saginaw Farmers Market & Saginaw Rec & Aquatics Center.
